Package: jiopc-agent
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-pip, python3-venv, xvfb, ca-certificates
Maintainer: Ambika <sambika1101@gmail.com>
Description: JioPC Automated Testing Agent
 Scripted validation framework that verifies web app reachability, native
 app health, and start menu / desktop app presence on a freshly patched
 JioPC OS Image. Produces a structured JSON Lines log consumed by a
 model-agnostic LLM analysis layer for a PROMOTE / HOLD recommendation.
 .
 This package installs the runner, three component modules, the default
 YAML configuration, and the LLM analysis prompt and script. Xvfb is
 pulled in as a runtime dependency for Part B GUI app isolation.
